OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fnight with rain spreading
OL,7,Fnortheastwards, heavy at times. Rain
OL,8,Fclearing all but eastern coasts by
OL,9,Fmorning. Winds becoming strong with
OL,10,Fcoastal gales before easing later in
OL,11,Fthe night.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FHeavy rain soon clearing to
OL,14,Fthe east to leave a largely dry day
OL,15,Fwith some bright spells and just the
OL,16,Fodd isolated shower. Light winds
OL,17,Fstrengthening in the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
